{"tid":2207161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"讓IU惦記了5年的粉絲再現身！還記得演唱會上大喊「胖什麼胖」的那位嗎XD","createTime":"2020-09-18T03:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T04:28:45.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4aeefaf3882583d19d2b15605656d3c746db98","tid":2207161,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_f8db4ced8aaccdf683478ef9aed993f8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130162-874165.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_f8db4ced8aaccdf683478ef9aed993f8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130162-874165.png&h=917ada63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經在演唱會上對IU大喊「胖什麼胖」的粉絲的近況再次受到了韓國網友們的熱烈關注，眾人狂呼「太羨慕了」。<br />\n<br />\n2015年11月，在釜山舉行演唱會的IU在與粉絲們的對話中說道：「因為說我胖了，所以...」這時，觀眾席上的某位女性粉絲忽然大聲高喊：「胖什麼胖！」聽得全場爆笑。 相關影片的點擊率高達650萬次，而這句「胖什麼胖」也成為了與IU有關的經典搜索詞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mB6MNl6uvmc&amp;feature=emb_err_woyt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmB6MNl6uvmc%26feature%3Demb_err_woyt&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=c081e982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mB6MNl6uvmc&amp;feature=emb_err_woyt</a><br />\nIU一直沒有忘記這位粉絲的「呐喊」，多次在公開場合提到過。 2017年發行的專輯《花書簽2》中，對於「10年活動期間最想用花書簽記下的2個瞬間是? 」，IU選擇了《秋日早晨》發售當天的心情和「胖什麼胖」。此外，IU還將「胖什麼胖」影片選為最佳影片，真的是印象太深刻了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4bd583618926a0281353436e3e2d6f29/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130162-874158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4bd583618926a0281353436e3e2d6f29%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130162-874158.jpg&h=f8c297d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2d4126735b10b2d6d1095bf741a44a52/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130162-874159.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2d4126735b10b2d6d1095bf741a44a52%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130162-874159.jpg&h=7bce6929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_da5e8fb320857ad5d1f20d8e6a45c7c0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130162-874161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_da5e8fb320857ad5d1f20d8e6a45c7c0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130162-874161.jpg&h=144878f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而今年5月，IU又一次提到了「胖什麼胖粉絲」，好奇對方是一個怎樣的人，引得這位粉絲親自留言回應IU，當時被大家羨慕追星成功。她還在IU的「尋人」影片裡再次現身，留言表示：「我是『胖什麼胖』本人， 知恩姐姐提到了我，我發文的手都在顫抖，我太幸福了。 能和IU生活在同一個時代，我感到非常幸福。 謝謝你給我聽這麼好的歌，會一直支持你，愛你。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_34e8888daa990e654c53a043b650a140/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-17/130162-874167.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_34e8888daa990e654c53a043b650a140%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-17%2F130162-874167.png&h=56d00955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n能被本命記住，這位「胖什麼胖粉絲」真的是追星成功了。<br />\n<br />\n原來段片已經咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c23406d94646deff568ff59a75f34472fca945","tid":2207161,"uid":372227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:28:45.000Z","msg":"IU認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}